19
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:10,560
I sent those voice messages.

20
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,920
He killed my daughter

21
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,200
and took my money.

22
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:16,870
I'd like to kill him.

23
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:22,070
[IOU]
In this column,

24
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:22,920
sign here.

25
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,230
We don't need

26
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,710
an IOU between us.

27
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,630
I can't owe anyone any more money,

28
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,840
especially you.

29
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,680
Sign it.

30
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:38,040
Keep it.

31
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,120
I'll pay you back as soon as I have it.

32
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,200
How can you pay me back?

33
00:03:44,230 --> 00:03:45,040
I'll borrow it.

34
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:47,870
For me?

35
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,320
You lost your mind?

36
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,280
Today, this guy showed mercy

37
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,200
and just chopped you twice.

38
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:52,990
But tomorrow,

39
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,200
what if they really want to kill you?

40
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,680
I'd rather owe them

41
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,870
than you.

42
00:03:57,990 --> 00:03:58,680
Sell my kidney.

43
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:00,840
I can sell my kidney to get it.

44
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,790
How much do you still owe those people?

45
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,760
It's none of your business.

46
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,310
How much do you still owe?

47
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,840
The principal is five million.

48
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:32,400
With interest,

49
00:04:33,350 --> 00:04:34,280
eight million.

50
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,910
I'll give you ten million.

51
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,120
Pay them back.

52
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:52,560
You can use the rest
to get back on your feet.

53
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,840
Okay?

54
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:56,750
No.

55
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,720
I've taken your money.

56
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,910
I can't take more.

57
00:05:00,790 --> 00:05:02,310
Count it as my investment
in your company.

58
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:03,960
I'll be a shareholder, okay?

59
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:07,630
You don't have that much money.

60
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:17,190
Don't worry about the money.

61
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,470
I'll figure it out.

