I'm looking for the contract
with Yangshi.

76
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,230
They want to adjust a detail.

77
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,510
What detail?

78
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,440
It's a little problem.

79
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,030
Just leave it to me.

80
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,160
It's in the third drawer.

81
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:27,470
Okay.

82
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:32,160
By the way, I'll have lunch with Mr. Gu.

83
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,190
How about you?

84
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,990
I'll just grab a bite to eat downstairs.

85
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,550
Remember to close the door for me.

86
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,040
Yes.

87
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:05,750
Did the money go to Fei Ke's account?

88
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,630
No.

89
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,110
He said his account was frozen.

90
00:09:10,110 --> 00:09:11,990
He told me to transfer the money
to another person's account.

91
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,510
And what happened

92
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:18,600
